The paper discusses security threats in machine learning-based systems, which is a topic related to cybersecurity (cs.CR). The paper also focuses on the use of machine learning for efficient processing of data, which falls under the category of machine learning (cs.LG). Additionally, the paper discusses the use of machine learning for image recognition tasks (MNIST and GTSRB), which is a subfield of computer vision (cs.CV). The paper also mentions the impact of security threats on hardware implementation, which is related to systems and control (cs.SY). Finally, the paper discusses the challenges in developing security measures for machine learning-based systems, which is related to artificial intelligence (cs.AI).
